ABOUT US
YR medical is an integrated industry and trade company focusing on medical device R&D, production, sales and consulting services. At present, the main products that are developed and sold are wheelchairs and medical beds, old-age scooters, walkers, toilet chairs, crutches, etc. We can provide OEM or ODM services according to the different needs of customers. At the same time, we can also recommend products that are popular among local market people based on our global market data analysis and sales. Our factory can provide you with a full range of purely customized services including brand, function, material, parts, etc., to ensure that it can meet the various customized needs of users; Our products are exported to Europe, America, South America, the Middle East and Southeast Asia and other global markets, and we have established in-depth cooperative relations with local distributors, charities, and medical rehabilitation institutions. Our professional technology and industry experience in the medical field are the Professional guarantee for cooperation and service.
Wheelchair
Kalstein YR medical wheelchair is our most advantageous product. We can provide wheelchairs with different functions for people with different needs, including electric wheelchairs, manual wheelchairs, wheelchairs for children with cerebral palsy, standing wheelchairs, stair climbing wheelchairs and other wheelchairs with different functions.
Electric medical bed
Kalstein YR medical electric medical bed is not only able to provide hospital beds, but also home care beds according to personal care needs. In terms of function, there are multiple functions such as electric turning, back lifting, leg lifting, lifting, and defecation to provide options to meet the needs of different scenes and users.
Manual Medical Bed
Kalstein YR medical manual medical bed is a cost-effective product series. According to the needs of different people, there are many functions such as turning over, lifting back, lifting legs, and releasing bowels. At the same time, to meet the needs of hospital beds, we also launched a series of nursing beds for families and individuals, giving customers more choices.
Product production process
  1. Purchase and inspection of raw materials and standard parts.
  2. Processing and inspection of outsourcing components.
  3. Mechanical processing and inspection of parts.
  4. Component assembly and inspection.
  5. Surface treatment and inspection of parts.
  6. Product assembly.
  7. Product inspection.
  8. Product packaging and product storage.
Note: The surface treatment baking varnish, spraying, and electroplating are all made by outsourcing.

Electric medical bed
Kalstein medical electric medical bed is not only able to provide hospital beds, but also home care beds according to personal care needs. In terms of function, there are multiple functions such as electric turning, back lifting, leg lifting, lifting, and defecation to provide options to meet the needs of different scenes and users.
Manual medical bed
Kalstein medical manual medical bed is a cost-effective product series. According to the needs of different people, there are many functions such as turning over, lifting back, lifting legs, and releasing bowels. At the same time, to meet the needs of hospital beds, we also launched a series of nursing beds for families and individuals, giving customers more choices.

At present, the main products that are developed and sold are wheelchairs and medical beds, old-age scooters, walkers, toilet chairs, crutches, etc. We can provide OEM or ODM services according to the different needs of customers. At the same time, we can also recommend products that are popular among local market people based on our global market data analysis and sales. Our factory can provide you with a full range of purely customized services including brand, function, material, parts, etc., to ensure that it can meet the various customized needs of users; Our products are exported to Europe, America, South America, the Middle East and Southeast Asia and other global markets, and we have established in-depth cooperative relations with local distributors, charities, and medical rehabilitation institutions. Our professional technology and industry experience in the medical field are the Professional guarantee for cooperation and service.
Wheelchair
Kalstein medical wheelchair is our most advantageous product. We can provide wheelchairs with different functions for people with different needs, including electric wheelchairs, manual wheelchairs, wheelchairs for children with cerebral palsy, standing wheelchairs, stair climbing wheelchairs and other wheelchairs with different functions.
Electric medical bed
Kalstein medical electric medical bed is not only able to provide hospital beds, but also home care beds according to personal care needs. In terms of function, there are multiple functions such as electric turning, back lifting, leg lifting, lifting, and defecation to provide options to meet the needs of different scenes and users.
Manual medical bed
Kalstein medical manual medical bed is a cost-effective product series. According to the needs of different people, there are many functions such as turning over, lifting back, lifting legs, and releasing bowels. At the same time, to meet the needs of hospital beds, we also launched a series of nursing beds for families and individuals, giving customers more choices.
Product production process:
  1. Purchase and inspection of raw materials and standard parts.
  2. Processing and inspection of outsourcing components.
  3. Mechanical processing and inspection of parts.
  4. Component assembly and inspection.
  5. Surface treatment and inspection of parts.
  6. Product assembly.
  7. Product inspection.
  8. Product packaging and product storage.
Note: The surface treatment baking varnish, spraying, and electroplating are all made by outsourcing.

Short description: Manufacturer: Kalstein\n\n
Description:
Electric climb stairs wheelchair YR05446, turns dreams into reality; with this unique device, you can explore the world like never before and bring a new taste to your everyday routines! The YR05446 wheelchair can help you climb stairs, overcome obstacles, and travel in any direction by using the one joystick on the side of the wheelchair.They are extremely popular because they’re easy to use and spare the users from having to use their arms to propel the chair. It also makes them less dependent on another person. These chairs are meant for everyone and can be especially useful for people with more serious disabilities who can’t propel a manual chair. The newest designs come with some amazing features such as a speech device, various controls, options to adapt the body position, and more.

Electric climb stairs wheelchair YR05446, long-range, lithium wheelchair is the best stair-climbing wheelchair overall. It comes with a big lithium battery and is three times faster than other power wheelchairs. It also works well on all kinds of stairs regardless of the texture.

Name: ATC Wine Refractometers YR05931 // YR05936
Short description: Manufacturer: Kalstein\n\n
Description:
The Wine Refractometer is a metal device that provides you with fast & accurate results. It's dual-scale provides you the direct reading of the alcohol as well as brix measurements. FULLY EQUIPPED with ATC that automatically adjust itself to correct temperature discrepancies during use. Refractive index is very temperature dependent; it is important to use a refractometer with automatic temperature compensation to give you the most accurate measurement in any type of environment temperature. Capable of measuring with high accuracy and provides precise results and is equipped with vivid and sharp reticle chart for easy and comfortable reading.
Features:
  • High quality body construction
  • Uses ambient light only which means battery or power source is not required
  • Easy to focus and calibrate
  • Cushioned with soft & comfortable non-slip rubber
  • With ATC function (Auto Temperature Compensation)
  • Durable and built to last long
